headline: PBCM Sold on Semiconductor (ON) Due to Persistent Downturn in EV Demand
summary: Pelican Bay Capital Management (PBCM), an investment management company, released its fourth-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. PBCM Concentrated Value Strategy returned 8.5% in the quarter, compared to a 3.8% return for the Russell 1000 Value Index.
